## What Was Built

### Project Structure

```
DriverLedger/
├── Helpers/
│   └── AppConstants.cs            ← DatabaseName constant
├── Models/
│   └── Company.cs                 ← SQLite table model
├── Database/
│   └── DatabaseService.cs         ← Async SQLite service, lazy init
├── Repositories/
│   ├── ICompanyRepository.cs      ← Contract
│   └── CompanyRepository.cs       ← Implementation
├── ViewModels/
│   ├── BaseViewModel.cs           ← INotifyPropertyChanged base
│   ├── LoginViewModel.cs          ← Login + navigation logic
│   ├── CompanyViewModel.cs        ← Company form + save logic
│   └── DashboardViewModel.cs      ← Company data loader
├── Views/
│   ├── LoginPage.xaml/cs          ← Dark blue themed login
│   ├── CompanyPage.xaml/cs        ← Green themed creation form
│   └── DashboardPage.xaml/cs      ← Card-based dashboard
├── App.xaml / App.xaml.cs         ← DI-injected AppShell + crash guard
├── AppShell.xaml / .cs            ← Shell routes registered
├── MauiProgram.cs                 ← Full DI container setup
└── Platforms/Android/
    ├── AndroidManifest.xml        ← Cleaned (offline-only, no INTERNET)
    └── MainApplication.cs         ← Global exception handlers
```

### Key Architecture Decisions

| Concern | Solution |
|---------|----------|
| Offline DB | `sqlite-net-pcl` + `SQLitePCLRaw.bundle_green` |
| Linker safety | `AndroidLinkMode=SdkOnly` in csproj |
| XAML inflation | `MauiXamlInflator=SourceGen` + `Runtime` override for resource dicts |
| DI | Full singleton/transient DI via [MauiProgram.cs](file:///g:/Application%20MAUI/New%20folder/Prototype%20DriverLedger/P1/DriverLedger/MauiProgram.cs) |
| Crash safety | Global `UnhandledException` + `UnobservedTaskException` handlers |
| Navigation | Shell routing — [LoginPage](file:///g:/Application%20MAUI/New%20folder/Prototype%20DriverLedger/P1/DriverLedger/Views/LoginPage.xaml.cs#5-16) as root, [CompanyPage](file:///g:/Application%20MAUI/New%20folder/Prototype%20DriverLedger/P1/DriverLedger/Views/CompanyPage.xaml.cs#5-16) + [DashboardPage](file:///g:/Application%20MAUI/New%20folder/Prototype%20DriverLedger/P1/DriverLedger/Views/DashboardPage.xaml.cs#5-22) as named routes |
| DB init | Pre-flight `Task.Run` before UI loads in [MauiProgram.cs](file:///g:/Application%20MAUI/New%20folder/Prototype%20DriverLedger/P1/DriverLedger/MauiProgram.cs) |

