## Errors Fixed During Build

| Error | Fix Applied |
|-------|------------|
| `CS0103 InitializeComponent` — 7 errors | Added `partial` to all XAML code-behind classes |
| `MAUIX2002 LetterSpacing` — 2 errors | Removed unsupported `LetterSpacing` from Labels |
| `Resources_Styles_*.sg.cs` sg.cs errors | Set `Inflator=Runtime` for [Colors.xaml](file:///g:/Application%20MAUI/New%20folder/Prototype%20DriverLedger/P1/DriverLedger/Resources/Styles/Colors.xaml) and [Styles.xaml](file:///g:/Application%20MAUI/New%20folder/Prototype%20DriverLedger/P1/DriverLedger/Resources/Styles/Styles.xaml) |
| `CS0618 DisplayAlert obsolete` — 10 warnings | Updated all ViewModels to `DisplayAlertAsync` |

