## App User Flow

```
Start
  └─▶ LoginPage (root)
        ├─▶ [Create Company] → CompanyPage
        │       └─▶ Fill form → Save → back to LoginPage
        └─▶ [Login] (email + password) → DashboardPage
                └─▶ Shows Company Name, Owner Name
                    ├─▶ Drivers card (Coming Soon)
                    ├─▶ Vehicles card (Coming Soon)
                    └─▶ Settlements card (Coming Soon)
```

