## 1 Remaining Warning (Non-blocking)

**XA0119** — *Using fast deployment and the linker at the same time is not recommended for Debug.*  
This is **expected** — the linker is set to `SdkOnly` for Release crash safety. In production Release builds this warning goes away. No action needed.
